gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Thunder 126, Mavericks 119
gameRecap.excerpt: Shai Gilgeous-Alexander leads the way with 31 points, nine rebounds and five assists as the Thunder defeat the Mavericks, 126-119. Jalen Williams added 27 points, four rebounds, five assists and 3 blocks in the victory, while Kyrie Irving tallied 36 points and 12 assists for the Mavericks in the losing effort. The Thunder improve to 46-20 on the season, while the Mavericks fall to 38-29.
